metadata.name: DEAD CAT BOUNCE #1
metadata.description: Welcome to the Dead Cat Bounce Trading Floor where culture meets Trading. A collection of 10 000 Dead Cats Bounce NFTs in the ETHEREUM blockchain built for the fearless and the mighty NFT and Crypto Traders. DCB is a community built ecosystem to enhance the knowledge and trading capacities of our community. Built by traders for traders. Becoming mainstream by partnering with global web2/web3 brands, Live events, NFT/Crypto training. Our goal is to create a community built for all market behaviors and simultaneously becoming recognized as the leading ETHEREUM community and brand. We bring Culture to Trading
